entries.journal_entry_description: Qakkee believes he's the greatest hunter in the galaxy. Prove that you are his equal!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Travel to Dantooine and hunt down more of the Voritor Lizards than Qakkee did. You need to bring back six horns as proof of your might.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Qakkee with the horns before the time runs out!
